-- China Evacuates 844 After Subsidence in Guangxi, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   L o u i s e   M e e s o n
-- 2012-06-02T12:30:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-02/china-evacuates-844-after-subsidence-in-guangxi-xinhua-reports.html
More than 800 people were evacuated
following land subsidence in south  China ’s Guangxi region, the
official Xinhua News Agency reported today, citing no one.  The subsidence took place near a middle school in Nanning
city’s Xixiangtang district after the school dug a well to ease
a water shortage, Xinhua said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
